{
  "stem": "14463.3",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we went to the other side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So there it was more civilized and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there, I enrolled into a proper school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], The Men's School of the name of Lenin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There I learned everything-- Russian, history, geography, geometry, everything else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, they provided for us-- I don't know why, and I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They provided for us a teacher, which was teaching us Polish, a Jewish man, which was teaching us Polish, which actually was a good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- there is one thing I've forgotten to tell you about the technical college, if I may go back--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--which stuck in my mind, is as the German armies were moving into Russia, the anti-Semitism become bigger and bigger.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in that school, in the technical college, I was going to school from 3 o'clock in the afternoon-- because it was in three shifts.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there were so may kids, they couldn't accommodate, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was three shifts, from 8:00 to 12:00, 12:00 to 3:00.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was from 3:00 till 8:00 in the evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a dark night, wintertime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was boys staying-- four or five boys was outside the sill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because it was downstairs, you know, the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were sharpening a knife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they said, we are waiting for you, you [NON-ENGLISH], you know, and we're going to finish you off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this I remember very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I got out of school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said, no, I'm going to stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So there was a Jewish boy together with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was two other Jewish boys in the class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, let's go to the teacher and the headmaster will take us home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, no way I'm going out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I got out.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
